{"tid":1756793,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"同我連根拔！港珠澳大橋顧問公司測試造假 12職員罪成 辯方求情：未出現安全問題","createTime":"2019-11-26T07:53:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T13:27:22.000Z","uid":74778,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"268600a532b8ac101c57ba9ca12270e58a7da71f","tid":1756793,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:53:19.000Z","msg":"為港珠澳大橋香港段測試石屎抗壓能力的嘉科工程顧問有限公司，多名實驗室技術員為隱瞞未能按時做測試，稱按上司指示造假，12人昨被裁定串謀詐騙罪成。辯方今求情指大橋尚未出現安全問題。法官李慶年卻指大橋花費5800萬公帑，又指倘若被告勤奮完成工作，定能如期完成測試，不過李體諒指「當然會有good times bad times，好似琴晚法庭要12點幾先做得曬」。案件押後至12月11日判刑，所有被告繼續關押。<br />\n<br />\n次被告吳啟堯的大狀求情指，吳身為本案污點證人應獲得一半的刑期扣減；雖然吳是本案的主導人物，而首被告麥培盛只負責「肯首」，惟吳的刑期理應低於麥，卻高於其他被告。<br />\n<br />\n官讚其中被告為人勤奮<br />\n<br />\n第三被告謝德禮的大狀求情指，被告於2012年確診患有抑鬱症以及適認障礙症，並一向於青山醫院接受治療。被告病情嚴重時更會有自殺傾向，審訊期間亦要增加服用藥量。此時被告於犯人欄指曾於還押期間要求取藥物但不果，稱「我好辛苦，頂唔順啦」。法官則表示對被告的供詞印象深刻，因被告為人勤奮，屢次「做埋人哋個份」。<br />\n<br />\n第七被告薜家俊的大狀求情透露，被告的父親欠債百多萬，被告需為父還債；被告亦為考取助理測量師牌照而努力進修，惟因本案而夢想幻滅。法官卻突然謂，認為此為減刑陳詞並非求情，「求情本係煽情，我有幾次動容，但上訴庭就話我唔跟依據判刑」。<br />\n<br />\n案件有18名被告，6人認罪，餘下受審的12名被告是小蠔灣工務試驗所的前實驗室技術員余維德、李詠暉、薛家俊、陳銳鏗、姚宇峰、葉德杰、吳汶鴻、張嘉明，及前實驗室助理謝德禮、李志勤、陳志成、郭文輝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191121/60293570?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191121%2F60293570%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV08v4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=b77d7f0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191121%2F60293570%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=464254f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191121/60293570?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n香港工程！又係比大陸毒撚到唔似人樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民意大爆發之後，真係要整頓呢d歪風！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上梁不正下樑歪！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etBWvd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetBWvd4.jpg&h=510fdab6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efe769923ee4b569bddd90f35416412b629e360e","tid":1756793,"uid":74171,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:54:43.000Z","msg":"未出現安全問題 = 遲啲會有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba974d160d559402f4b37d312c2a3df4811c0a8a","tid":1756793,"uid":55384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:56:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b907ee0986b69f252b880c6b42bfd7e2b16f2ae","tid":1756793,"uid":266207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"仲有沙中線一系列豆腐渣工程，一定要追究"},{"pid":"1535e58cbf67a09eec407c457cd281e4ff748b55","tid":1756793,"uid":124180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:57:33.000Z","msg":"港豬澳大橋遲撚早散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08482b76e8d53e98505d80e2d76a3f7f4d398b88","tid":1756793,"uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b907ee0986b69f252b880c6b42bfd7e2b16f2ae","tid":1756793,"uid":266207,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:57:17.000Z","msg":"仲有沙中線一系列豆腐渣工程，一定要追究"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:57:48.000Z","msg":"梁生，死出黎埋單啦"},{"pid":"770