t-align: right;\"><blockquote><br />\n    [香港立法會選舉備戰] 學習美國民主黨<br />\n如何為2020年總統大選總動員<br />\n    - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n    <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756444\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756444</a><br />\n</div></blockquote>"},{"pid":"dd753149686ac86b2d6d7bad368150bce00e01c5","tid":1756793,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:33:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afda3331e09b08a59aa4d733089e3564c1a56f87","tid":1756793,"uid":182185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:35:07.000Z","msg":"Jacobs<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"012df9174f189e8e0d8991ef3f59e5534422cd80","tid":1756793,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"770437367051684cfcd0390557d6c74ac39b1fe0","tid":1756793,"uid":266755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"268600a532b8ac101c57ba9ca12270e58a7da71f","tid":1756793,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:53:19.000Z","msg":"為港珠澳大橋香港段測試石屎抗壓能力的嘉科工程顧問有限公司，多名實驗室技術員為隱瞞未能按時做測試，稱按上司指示造假，12人昨被裁定串謀詐騙罪成。辯方今求情指大橋尚未出現安全問題。法官李慶年卻指大橋花費5800萬公帑，又指倘若被告勤奮完成工作，定能如期完成測試，不過李體諒指「當然會有good times bad times，好似琴晚法庭要12點幾先做得曬」。案件押後至12月11日判刑，所有被告繼續關押。<br />\n<br />\n次被告吳啟堯的大狀求情指，吳身為本案污點證人應獲得一半的刑期扣減；雖然吳是本案的主導人物，而首被告麥培盛只負責「肯首」，惟吳的刑期理應低於麥，卻高於其他被告。<br />\n<br />\n官讚其中被告為人勤奮<br />\n<br />\n第三被告謝德禮的大狀求情指，被告於2012年確診患有抑鬱症以及適認障礙症，並一向於青山醫院接受治療。被告病情嚴重時更會有自殺傾向，審訊期間亦要增加服用藥量。此時被告於犯人欄指曾於還押期間要求取藥物但不果，稱「我好辛苦，頂唔順啦」。法官則表示對被告的供詞印象深刻，因被告為人勤奮，屢次「做埋人哋個份」。<br />\n<br />\n第七被告薜家俊的大狀求情透露，被告的父親欠債百多萬，被告需為父還債；被告亦為考取助理測量師牌照而努力進修，惟因本案而夢想幻滅。法官卻突然謂，認為此為減刑陳詞並非求情，「求情本係煽情，我有幾次動容，但上訴庭就話我唔跟依據判刑」。<br />\n<br />\n案件有18名被告，6人認罪，餘下受審的12名被告是小蠔灣工務試驗所的前實驗室技術員余維德、李詠暉、薛家俊、陳銳鏗、姚宇峰、葉德杰、吳汶鴻、張嘉明，及前實驗室助理謝德禮、李志勤、陳志成、郭文輝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191121/60293570?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191121%2F60293570%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=%2BSgL3cCD37R2%2BMUJ9ALV08v4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=b77d7f0b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191121%2F60293570%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=464254f2\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191121/60293570?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n<br />\n香港工程！又係比大陸毒撚到唔似人樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n民意大爆發之後，真係要整頓呢d歪風！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">上梁不正下樑歪！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/etBWvd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FetBWvd4.jpg&h=510fdab6&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T07:59:25.000Z","msg":"一早都知佢唔俾啲lorry行都有啲鬼。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:36:27.000Z","msg":"唔係比行但攞permit麻煩又貴咋咩"},{"pid":"993c0956bed353583a26e63ffeb62caa66b0fd10","tid":1756793,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:40:06.000Z","msg":"【公投】12.1 舉行九區同步遊行！誠邀曾經舉辦地區遊行搞手入紙申請！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756851\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756851</a>"},{"pid":"0c4f8668a6456